<view class="container invitations-page">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <text class="hero-eyebrow">USport / 消息工作区</text>
    <text class="hero-title">把邀约、进度提醒和关键信息收进一个稳定入口。</text>
    <text class="hero-subtitle">
      这里优先展示真正影响成局和履约的消息，而不是做一个泛聊天列表。
    </text>

    <view class="hero-metrics">
      <view class="metric-card">
        <text class="metric-value">{{workspace.pendingCount}}</text>
        <text class="metric-label">待处理邀约</text>
      </view>
      <view class="metric-card">
        <text class="metric-value">{{workspace.unreadCount}}</text>
        <text class="metric-label">未读提醒</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{!isLoggedIn}}" class="empty-card">
    <text class="empty-title">登录后查看你的消息工作区</text>
    <text class="empty-text">
      邀约、活动进度和履约提醒都会汇总到这里，帮助你更稳地安排运动节奏。
    </text>
    <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="onGoLogin">去登录</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:elif="{{loading}}" class="loading-card">
    <text class="loading-text">正在同步消息工作区...</text>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="section-card">
      <view class="section-header">
        <text class="section-title">待处理邀约</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">优先处理会影响你本周运动安排的邀约。</text>
      </view>

      <view wx:if="{{workspace.invitations.length === 0}}" class="empty-inline">
        <text class="empty-inline-title">还没有新的邀约</text>
        <text class="empty-inline-text">当别人邀请你加入活动时，会优先出现在这里。</text>
      </view>

      <view wx:else class="card-list">
        <view
          class="invite-card"
          wx:for="{{workspace.invitations}}"
          wx:key="id"
          bindtap="onInvitationTap"
          data-activity-id="{{item.activityId}}"
          hover-class="card-hover"
        >
          <view class="card-top">
            <view class="card-copy">
              <text class="card-title">{{item.activityTitle}}</text>
              <text class="card-meta">{{item.venueLabel}}</text>
            </view>
            <text class="status-badge">{{item.statusLabel}}</text>
          </view>
          <text class="card-message">{{item.message}}</text>
          <text class="card-meta">{{item.senderName}} · {{item.senderBadge}}</text>
          <text class="card-meta">{{item.activityTime}} · {{item.participantHint}}</text>

          <view wx:if="{{item.canAccept || item.canDecline}}" class="action-row">
            <button
              wx:if="{{item.canDecline}}"
              class="ghost-btn"
              size="mini"
              catchtap="onRespondTap"
              data-id="{{item.id}}"
              data-action="decline"
            >
              婉拒
            </button>
            <button
              wx:if="{{item.canAccept}}"
              class="primary-btn"
              size="mini"
              catchtap="onRespondTap"
              data-id="{{item.id}}"
              data-action="accept"
            >
              接受邀约
            </button>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card">
      <view class="section-header">
        <text class="section-title">最近消息</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">汇总邀约状态变化和活动提醒。</text>
      </view>

      <view wx:if="{{workspace.messages.length === 0}}" class="empty-inline">
        <text class="empty-inline-title">还没有新的消息</text>
        <text class="empty-inline-text">等你收到邀约和活动更新后，这里会逐步形成稳定消息流。</text>
      </view>

      <view wx:else class="card-list">
        <view
          class="message-card"
          wx:for="{{workspace.messages}}"
          wx:key="id"
          bindtap="onMessageTap"
          data-id="{{item.id}}"
          hover-class="card-hover"
        >
          <view class="card-top">
            <text class="card-title">{{item.title}}</text>
            <text class="message-time">{{item.timestampLabel}}</text>
          </view>
          <text class="card-message">{{item.preview}}</text>
          <view wx:if="{{item.unreadCount > 0}}" class="message-badge">
            {{item.unreadCount}} 条未读
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
